 17171, \"end\": 17189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jakob Ingebrigtsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ingebrigtsen won gold in the grueling 5000m in Paris, and he also won gold in the 1500m in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 17192, \"to\": 17289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17239, \"end\": 17244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1166910632794817e-31, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 17283, \"end\": 17288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3106649576073866e-13, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr is the defending world champion, but none of that matters when you can do this:  WOW.\", \"from\": 17290, \"to\": 17380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17376, \"end\": 17379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_of_Wrestling\", \"score\": 0.9301971564647867, \"rank\": 0.03907868838041944, \"text\": \"WOW\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_of_Wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_of_Wrestling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00b1A STUNNING upset in the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 1500m as AMERICAN COLE HOCKER takes gold!#ParisOlympicspic.twitter.com/wlq81lbvSO  Team USA is the preeminent Olympic powerhouse.\", \"from\": 17381, \"to\": 17546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17435, \"end\": 17446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \